apiParam.apiDesc:
An array of functions that accept a value from the previous sequence and 
		        return a new sequence:
		        function (value : T) : IObservable

A function that will be called for each value from the left ("this") and will 
		     return the IObservable that represents the lifetime window of that value:
		     function(left:TLeft):IObservable

A function that will be called for each value from right and will 
		     return the IObservable that represents the lifetime window of that value:
		     function(right:TRight):IObservable

